128 the respondent thus contravened s 298k(1)(a) of the act by dismissing mr coon and mr kemmis for reasons which included reasons prohibited by s 298l(1)(a) and (l), and by dismissing mr taylor for reasons which included the reason prohibited by s 298l(1)(l) of the act.
